$content = '<p>水电阶段1<img src="https://qimg.mama.cn/home/diary/2018/11/4e5c5428aca559afc754cb033d8bea_w300X190_w196X124.jpg" title="decoration2.jpg" alt="decoration2.jpg"/></p><p>你好，姚明<br/><img src="https://qimg.mama.cn/home/diary/2018/11/18e15e5a8a943158e9298403aa2df1_w300X208_w196X135.jpg" title="decoration.jpg" alt="decoration.jpg"/></p><audio controls="controls" style="display: none;"></audio>';

